| File | Scope |
|------|--------|
| `engineering-guardrails.mdc` | Architecture, OpenSpec, SPECBOOT gates |
| `specboot-workflow.mdc` | Stage detection and command order |
| `github-workflow.mdc` | Branches, issues, status, milestones, views, PRs |
| `.github/PROJECT.md` | Project board setup and view recipes |
